---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /contact/
title: Contact — Piment Catering
description: Neem contact op met Piment Catering — vragen, dieetwensen, allergieën of feedback. We horen graag van je.

hero_label: We horen graag van je
hero_title: Piment hoort graag van je!
hero_text: Heb je een vraag, wensen voor je dieet of allergieën, of wil je gewoon iets laten weten? Stuur een berichtje en we nemen zo snel mogelijk contact met je op.

form_title: Laat je reactie achter
success_message: Bedankt, we nemen zo snel mogelijk contact met je op!
---

<section class="section container" style="max-width: 1000px; padding-top: var(--spacing-12);">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-16);">
    <span class="label-md" style="color: var(--secondary);">{{ hero_label }}</span>
    <h1 class="display-lg" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-4); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">{{ hero_title }}</h1>
    <p class="body-lg" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">{{ hero_text }}</p>
  </div>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-16); align-items: start;">

    <div>
      <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">Gegevens</h3>

      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
        <span class="label-md" style="color: var(--tertiary);">{{ site.lunchcafe_address.name }}</span>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); margin-bottom: 0;">{{ site.lunchcafe_address.location }}</p>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-bottom: 0;">{{ site.lunchcafe_address.street }}, {{ site.lunchcafe_address.city }}</p>
        <p class="body-lg" style="color: var(--secondary); margin-top: var(--spacing-2);">{{ site.lunchcafe_address.hours }}</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
        <span class="label-md" style="color: var(--tertiary);">Direct contact</span>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); margin-bottom: 0;">
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}" style="color: var(--on-surface); text-decoration: underline;">{{ site.contact.email }}</a>
        </p>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phone_link }}" style="color: var(--on-surface);">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
        <span class="label-md" style="color: var(--tertiary);">Postadres</span>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); margin-bottom: 0;">{{ site.postal_address.street }}</p>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-bottom: 0;">{{ site.postal_address.postcode }} {{ site.postal_address.city }}</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <span class="label-md" style="color: var(--tertiary);">KvK</span>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); margin-bottom: 0;">{{ site.kvk }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="padding: var(--spacing-12);">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">{{ form_title }}</h3>
      <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/contact/?success=true">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
        <p hidden><label>Niet invullen: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
          <label class="input-label">Naam</label>
          <input type="text" name="name" class="input-field" required>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
          <label class="input-label">E-mail</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" class="input-field" required>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
          <label class="input-label">Bericht</label>
          <textarea name="message" class="input-field" rows="5" required style="resize: vertical;"></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem;">Verstuur</button>
      </form>

      <p id="success-message" class="label-md" style="display: none; color: var(--secondary); margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">{{ success_message }}</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script>
  if (new URLSearchParams(window.location.search).get('success') === 'true') {
    var msg = document.getElementById('success-message');
    if (msg) msg.style.display = 'block';
  }
</script>
